<p>Breaking deep material into smaller bits makes sense to me. I&#8217;m currently <a href="http://hackprose.org" rel="nofollow">writing</a> about my progress through <a href="http://mitpress.mit.edu/sicp/full-text/book/book-Z-H-4.html#%_toc_start" rel="nofollow">SICP</a> and have found working on one concept at a time is tractable.</p>

